		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><small> <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=0.E_(Ellison)" title="0.E (Ellison)">‚Äπ‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî 0.E</a> &#8195; <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=0.C_(Cooper)" title="0.C (Cooper)">0.C ‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Ä∫</a> </small> <br />
0.D (Danny) is a version of Cataclysm that was released on March 8, 2019.
</p>
